{"tid":1567941,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"再下星期遊行主題係支持美國政府制裁何君妖","createTime":"2019-09-14T07:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T07:52:43.000Z","uid":289565,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ec72974ceedd244840c96e200175a5542b9e468c","tid":1567941,"uid":289565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:49:43.000Z","msg":"先講下點解個主題係咁 <br />\n係人都知何妖同支聯辦有關係 如果美國首先制裁佢既話 既可以嚇一下支聯辦 又可以避免同支共關係太惡化 <br />\n<br />\n何妖同黑社會有關 佢被制之後應該會少左堆黑社會出黎搞事 <br />\n<br />\n最後 係再一次要求美國國會盡快通過人權法<br />\n 而家支共吹風話要控制香港 支那加又話要收購倫交所 佢地明顯係想盡快控制香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我地要再次希望美國國會盡快定立人權法"},{"pid":"ebac6595be140c15eefc64b4a3f483fb8de33ea7","tid":1567941,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:52:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}